doc.title: Kōllaajrak in Link eo Open With extension
doc.description:
Extension in ej kōtlok am maroñ in lale ewi wawein an hyperlink ko bellok.

Window: browser ko jet, window ko rej walok, window ko rekãl, window ko rekãl, window eo kiõ (default)

Tabs: anbijmaroñ in tab eo kiõ, tab eo kiõ, anbijmaroñ in tab eo kiõ (default)

Activation state: jab jerbal, activate immediately (default)
